| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5595 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 47bb4d6a-5e71-517d-8bce-1511769cf5fb"
